Cs_number13_final - A map by Anthony Irtelli

Final release. Fixed some balance and optimisation issues. Up to 48 players.

Terrorists having taken scientists from FearCorp hostage in an empty house that happens to be number 13.

Many thanks to all of those people who I've unwittingly taken textures and models from.

Go to rustyinplaces.org and play this on our css server!
